Formula for the Digital Root
 (n)=0,if n=0
 (n)=9,if n=9k
 (n)=nmod9,if n=9k
 
 Question ---------->   38
 step 1. 3+8=11
 step 2. 1+1=2
 answer is 2
 
 
 code 
 
 class Solution {
    public int addDigits(int num) {
        if (num == 0) return 0;
        if (num % 9 == 0) return 9;
        return num % 9;
    }
}
